src/components/molecules/PageFooter/Page.description:
The PageFooter is the main footer on the page, and should be included only once.
It contains a small number of important, side-wide links.

src/components/molecules/PageHeader/Page.description:
The PageHeader is the main header on the page, and should be included only once.
It contains the Telia logo, the main navigation, and tools such as log-in info
and shopping cart.
